\f2\b0 For new installations, during installation create a custom partition setup and specify a\
separate partition for 
\f0 \cf4 /home
\f2 \cf2 .\
For systems that were previously installed, create a new partition and configure\

\f0 \cf4 /etc/fstab
\f2 \cf2  as appropriate.\

