\f4\i0\fs20\fsmilli10080 RPM: gpg-pubkey-9db62fb1-59920156\
Packager: Fedora 28 (28) <fedora-28@fedoraproject.org>\
Summary: gpg(Fedora 28 (28) <fedora-28@fedoraproject.org>)\
Creation date: 2017-08-14\
Key ID: 9db62fb1\
RPM: gpg-pubkey-09eab3f2-595fbba3\
Packager: RPM Fusion free repository for Fedora (28) <rpmfusion-\
buildsys@lists.rpmfusion.org>\
Summary: gpg(RPM Fusion free repository for Fedora (28) <rpmfusion-\
buildsys@lists.rpmfusion.org>)\
Creation date: 2017-07-07\
Key ID: 09eab3f2\

\f2\fs24 The format of the package (
\f0 \cf4 gpg-pubkey-9db62fb1-59920156
\f2 \cf2 ) is important to\
understand for verification. Using the above example, it consists of three parts:\
1. The general prefix name for all imported GPG keys: 
\f0 \cf4 gpg-pubkey-\

\f2 \cf2 2. The version, which is the GPG key ID: 
\f0 \cf4 9db62fb1\

\f2 \cf2 3. The release is the date of the key in UNIX timestamp in hexadecimal: 
\f0 \cf4 59920156
