\f2\b0 Not all repositories, notably RedHat, support 
\f0 \cf4 repo_gpgcheck
\f2 \cf2 . Take care to set this\
value to false (default) for particular repositories that do not support it. If enabled on\
repositories that do not support 
\f0 \cf4 repo_gpgcheck
\f2 \cf2  installation of packages will fail.\
Research is required by the user to determine which repositories are configured on the\
local system and, from that list, which support 
\f0 \cf4 repo_gpgcheck
\f2 \cf2 .\

