\f3\i\fs32\fsmilli16080 \cf3 1.3.1.4 Ensure the SELinux mode is not disabled (Automated)\

\f1\i0\b\fs24 \cf2 Profile Applicability:\

\f0\b0 \'95
\f2  Level 1 - Server\

\f0 \'95
