\f3\i\fs32\fsmilli16080 \cf3 1.3.1.5 Ensure the SELinux mode is enforcing (Automated)\

\f1\i0\b\fs24 \cf2 Profile Applicability:\

\f0\b0 \'95
\f2  Level 2 - Server\

\f0 \'95
