\f1\b Description:\

\f2\b0 This variable limits the types of MAC algorithms that SSH can use during\
communication.\

\f1\b Note:\

\f0\b0\fs20\fsmilli10080 \'95
\f2  
\fs24 Some organizations may have stricter requirements for approved MACs.\

\f0\fs20\fsmilli10080 \'95
\f2  
\fs24 Ensure that MACs used are in compliance with site policy.\

\f0\fs20\fsmilli10080 \'95
