\f2 \cf2  - Enable feature "implied-feature"\
if feature "feature" is enabled. The whole line with this operator is removed, thus\
it is not possible to add anything else around this operator at the same line.\

\f0\fs20\fsmilli10080 \'95
\f2  
\f0\fs24 \cf4 \{if "feature":true|false\}
\f2 \cf2  - If "feature" is defined, replace this operator with\
string "true", otherwise with string "false".\

\f0\fs20\fsmilli10080 \'95
\f2  
\f0\fs24 \cf4 \{if "feature":true\}
\f2 \cf2  - If "feature" is defined, replace this operator with string\
"true", otherwise with an empty string.\

