\f4\fs20\fsmilli10080 o
\f2  
\fs24 This new style format is specifically targeted towards more advanced use\
cases like forwarding to remote hosts that might be partially offline.\

\f0\fs20\fsmilli10080 \'95
\f2  
\f0\fs24 \cf4 obsolete legacy
\f2 \cf2  - previously known simply as the 
\f0 \cf4 legacy
\f2 \cf2  format, this format is\
