\f2 \cf2 .\

\f1\b Rationale:\

\f2\b0 The 
\f0 \cf4 /etc/passwd
\f2 \cf2  file also contains information like user ID's and group ID's that are\
used by many system programs. Therefore, the 
\f0 \cf4 /etc/passwd
\f2 \cf2  file must remain world\
